{"tid":2494782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企個MCB間歇性跳制","createTime":"2021-04-18T19:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T02:09:35.000Z","uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a16ad607226e395493d4c09255d5d5e6760562a4","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇巴打知跳制點搞<br />\n諗住試埋聽朝,搞唔掂再搵師傅<br />\n屋企大功率同設計簡單果D電器差唔多試曬<br />\n(不過蚊完都未解決到個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n呢家試淨電腦同差手機果D火牛<br />\n講多少少測試果陣，除非一啪個掣就即刻熄，如果唔係部電腦都著緊（趕緊功課），之後頂到一陣(大約45mins-3hours)，之後就會再跳<br />\n以我理解如果跳制關電腦事，都要過一段時間先會跳，所以點先知道跳掣係關電腦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMCB跳掣嗰粒係插蘇掣"},{"pid":"26a252625be01e1cf63a721b7a0e4b06536d389d","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a16ad607226e395493d4c09255d5d5e6760562a4","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇巴打知跳制點搞<br />\n諗住試埋聽朝,搞唔掂再搵師傅<br />\n屋企大功率同設計簡單果D電器差唔多試曬<br />\n(不過蚊完都未解決到個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n呢家試淨電腦同差手機果D火牛<br />\n講多少少測試果陣，除非一啪個掣就即刻熄，如果唔係部電腦都著緊（趕緊功課），之後頂到一陣(大約45mins-3hours)，之後就會再跳<br />\n以我理解如果跳制關電腦事，都要過一段時間先會跳，所以點先知道跳掣係關電腦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMCB跳掣嗰粒係插蘇掣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:25:56.000Z","msg":"同埋MCB用左30年未換過<br />\n諗住聽日再試一次<br />\n其實有冇方法易D搵到電器衰定mcb衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b638670f828a7450c0448db0562fcd8cbbdaae","tid":2494782,"uid":44691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:26:11.000Z","msg":"係買咗新電腦一插電用落就咁樣定點？"},{"pid":"4d306c54e791b5cd8eeef4fb02a80aebb89a2365","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b638670f828a7450c0448db0562fcd8cbbdaae","tid":2494782,"uid":44691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:26:11.000Z","msg":"係買咗新電腦一插電用落就咁樣定點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:32:46.000Z","msg":"部電腦low profile枱機來，個火牛半年前壞咗，拎咗去電腦舖度整唔知關唔關事，見佢換返個火牛都似之前廠機個隻，唔排除係老番<br />\n<br />\n部電腦喺跳完制再著番過制後後，通常都著咗一段時間個制先會再跳，所以真係唔知關唔關事"},{"pid":"677e21bf2f5646f1e9c9508a12d184dd91e97086","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:37:34.000Z","msg":"呢家最撚慘係，次撚次跳完制蚊完D電器後，隔一段時間先再跳過（懷疑未搵到源頭）"},{"pid":"5cd3fbea3cfc7ccca9c15063518ca8002960c264","tid":2494782,"uid":44691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:42:45.000Z","msg":"1. 唔著電腦 但照著其他電器<br />\n2. 著電腦 但著少1~2樣電器<br />\n睇下會唔會跳？<br />\n<br />\n唔建議咁快搵師傅 因為mcb好少壞 況且又唔係唔識跳"},{"pid":"3ecfdf8295c0592e5ae0a895c926ab7bb67ac0bc","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd3fbea3cfc7ccca9c15063518ca8002960c264","tid":2494782,"uid":44691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:42:45.000Z","msg":"1. 唔著電腦 但照著其他電器<br />\n2. 著電腦 但著少1~2樣電器<br />\n睇下會唔會跳？<br />\n<br />\n唔建議咁快搵師傅 因為mcb好少壞 況且又唔係唔識跳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:44:44.000Z","msg":"明白，聽日再試<br />\nThanks,巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.