like":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"樓主都努力過，建議你搵A牌師傅搞搞佢，相信專業，免生意外<br />\n以下我見解<br />\n1. 俾張圖<br />\n2. MCB通常1000秒以上trip都好唔common，所以只要求你檢查下你上述時間先會運行的用具e.g. 定時翻煲熱水爐<br />\n3. 有翻咁上下樓齡，有機會mcb壞要換，但最好揾師傅搞，有電危險"},{"pid":"6a88192976bc7ac33b91974aa293ab96a431b5e5","tid":2494782,"uid":133217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:21:06.000Z","msg":"check下牆同天花有冇濕"},{"pid":"5451aac0f28fb2ce00f757a5a0a2386555f4d19c","tid":2494782,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"留意屋企有冇一D拖板或蘇位濕咗水<br />\n係咪用緊電煲煲湯？<br />\n<br />\n電腦試下插第二個蘇位或拖板"},{"pid":"a2b05374b14ae0ae788c948c72298baa9798b655","tid":2494782,"uid":209662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:32:45.000Z","msg":"遂樣電器試。。"},{"pid":"ba5bb3fe62ecc12daef0d53062437acdc2cd4ade","tid":2494782,"uid":265291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:34:39.000Z","msg":"可能個RCBO 感應到過熱 跳"},{"pid":"b5fe467574925f23b83e6819faaaf7204c171875","tid":2494782,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"點解關電腦事 係會過一段時間先跳？ 邊到聽返黎<br />\n雪櫃熱水爐都係定時會行既電器"},{"pid":"34145d81ad9e0d98316e1c53eb86444444659091","tid":2494782,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:43:19.000Z","msg":"好難check唔知有冇線皮損左，落左地"},{"pid":"00a24474fb2c04e715f801a82c436b9e4c704937","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:44:30.000Z","msg":"更新宜家過情況<br />\n朝早個陣又跳左次，懷疑因為源頭漏電<br />\n之後蚊曬全屋嗰啲拖板插蘇<br />\n之後等左五分鐘(五分鐘之前就算蚊曬所有電器都著唔返個漏電斷路器)，再開得返著過漏電斷路器<br />\n呢家繼續最後測試中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTMsjZ7DPosT8NZMH3J15y67QkC7oSDdoJQPN45kLJWvK?filename=JZANqVf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZANqVf.jpg&h=d45a7ef5&s={